include ../includes/head.pug
include ../includes/headerEng.pug
include ../includes/sliderEng.pug
include ../includes/footerEng.pug

doctype html
html(lang='en')
  +head('../','VIDEO 27')
  link(rel="stylesheet", href="../css/ekko-lightbox.css")
  body
    +header("../")
    main
      +slider('../')
      .container.videos
        .row.mx-auto
          .col
            h3 VIDEO 27
            h4 Female Beach Wrestling. Part 2. June,  2011
            p.
              This is a continuation of the multi-round sand-wrestling contest between  <b>Tais</b>  (5'7" / 130 lb) and  <b>Elena Vasilyeva</b>  (5'6" / 135 lb). The first nine rounds of this exciting match were featured in our Video 26 (scroll the page down a little to see the initial description). Here in the Part 2 you can see eight more rounds fought with the same rules as those in the Part 1.
            img.mainImg(src='../img/videos/27/2011-female-beach-wrestling-2.jpg' alt='2011-female-beach-wrestling-2')
            p.
              Although both women are very ambitious, they are not quite equal in experience and skill. One of them is still using some nice wrestling combinations, applying good choking and submission holds, while the other is just struggling heavily, showing her fighting spirit and refusing to give up.
            p If you like strong, skilled and athletic women in real wrestling, then we recommend you to purchase this video.
            a.btn.btn-primary.screensBtn(data-toggle='collapse' href='#collapseExample' role='button' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample')
              | SCREENSHOTS
            #collapseExample.collapse
              .col-md-12.text-center
                  .row.justify-content-center
                    - var n = 0;
                    while n < 38
                      - n = n+1
                      a.col-sm-4(href='../img/videos/27/'+n+'.jpg' data-toggle='lightbox' data-gallery='example-gallery')
                        img.img-fluid(src='../img/videos/27/'+n+'.jpg')
            hr
            p.
              You can buy <b>VIDEO 27</b> on <a href='https://gumroad.com/namazonclub'>Gumroad</a>.
    +footer("../")